done

properties.scriptBody:
ln -s /opt/tradeapp/${p:version.name} /opt/tradeapp/latest
chmod a+x  /opt/tradeapp/latest/bin/injector.sh
chmod a+x  /opt/tradeapp/latest/bin/server.sh
service TradeappSS start

sleep 20
if curl -s http://localhost:8080/trades/stats | grep "totalTrades"
then
    echo "all good"
else
    exit 1
fi
